00:05:10,750 --> 00:05:11,240
Bravo!

54
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:12,360
Bravo!

55
00:05:13,660 --> 00:05:14,370
Something's not right.

56
00:05:21,080 --> 00:05:22,080
What's going on?

57
00:05:22,870 --> 00:05:24,070
Wasn't she dancing just fine a moment ago?

58
00:05:24,090 --> 00:05:24,800
That's right.

59
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:30,680
Quick, take a look, take a look.

60
00:05:34,950 --> 00:05:35,550
Don't be afraid.

61
00:05:35,870 --> 00:05:36,560
Whatever I ask,

62
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:37,510
just answer accordingly.

63
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:38,920
What was your relationship

64
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:40,120
with the deceased?

65
00:05:40,150 --> 00:05:41,240
We have no relationship.

66
00:05:41,430 --> 00:05:42,600
We just arrived here not long ago.

67
00:05:42,830 --> 00:05:43,480
Listen to me.

68
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:44,600
As she was spinning, she suddenly collapsed.

69
00:05:46,830 --> 00:05:47,600
Someone's died.

70
00:05:51,870 --> 00:05:53,270
Before Tian Rui, the deceased, went on stage,

71
00:05:53,830 --> 00:05:54,920
who had seen her?

72
00:05:56,830 --> 00:05:57,310
Officer,

73
00:05:57,630 --> 00:05:58,600
I'm not sure.

74
00:05:59,190 --> 00:06:00,950
The backstage is off-limits to outsiders.

75
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:02,120
It should be

76
00:06:02,170 --> 00:06:03,750
only people from their dance troupe, I guess.

77
00:06:07,430 --> 00:06:08,600
