78
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:10,630
Yes.

79
00:06:11,330 --> 00:06:12,040
This way, please.

80
00:06:12,070 --> 00:06:12,570
Lead the way.

81
00:06:22,070 --> 00:06:22,630
Officer.

82
00:06:23,210 --> 00:06:23,970
This was where Tian Rui

83
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:24,720
did her makeup.

84
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:27,240
I see.

85
00:06:27,630 --> 00:06:28,240
You can go out first.

86
00:06:28,630 --> 00:06:29,120
Yes.

87
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:37,470
Chief Constable Wen,

88
00:06:38,310 --> 00:06:38,870
Chief Chu said

89
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:40,040
to bring the deceased's belongings

90
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:41,070
to the government office for examination.

91
00:06:41,409 --> 00:06:41,920
Alright.

92
00:06:42,520 --> 00:06:43,150
Oh, right.

93
00:06:43,630 --> 00:06:44,770
bring everyone outside

94
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:45,880
back for questioning later.

95
00:06:46,070 --> 00:06:46,510
Understood.

96
00:06:59,830 --> 00:07:00,240
My lord.

97
00:07:00,830 --> 00:07:01,430
What's the situation?

98
00:07:02,480 --> 00:07:03,000
My lord,

99
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:05,070
the deceased was a dancer from Yunmen Dance Troupe.

100
00:07:05,230 --> 00:07:06,430
She suddenly died on stage during the performance.

101
00:07:08,830 --> 00:07:09,600
Tian Rui?

102
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:11,390
Do you know her?

103
00:07:14,040 --> 00:07:14,870
More than a decade ago,

104
00:07:15,680 --> 00:07:16,850
I had a brief encounter

105
00:07:16,950 --> 00:07:17,920
with her.

106
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:20,750
Her performance of the Xi River Formation

107
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:22,350
was as graceful as a dragon.

108
00:07:22,510 --> 00:07:24,360
The audience was massive and the cheers were thunderous.

109
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:26,070
Even now, thinking back,

110
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:27,920
it's still vivid in my mind.

111
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:30,160
I never thought...

112
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:32,950
More than a decade ago?

113
00:07:33,940 --> 00:07:35,060
She must have been quite young, right?

114
00:07:35,750 --> 00:07:36,120
Yes.

115
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:38,040
She was in her twenties,

116
00:07:38,510 --> 00:07:40,480
the prime of a woman's life.

117
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:57,510
Well...

118
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:58,890
Is this the Tian Rui

119
00:07:58,920 --> 00:07:59,680
that you know?

120
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:01,310
Yes,

121
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:02,610
indeed,

122
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:03,830
but

123
00:08:04,830 --> 00:08:06,680
more than a decade has passed.

124
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:08,360
Why hasn't her appearance

125
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:09,630
changed at all?

126
00:08:10,070 --> 00:08:10,480
My lord,

127
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:12,600
I've heard that the women in dance troupes

128
00:08:12,630 --> 00:08:13,750
all have their own secret methods for maintaining their youth.

129
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:15,390
Combined with makeup and attire,

130
00:08:15,750 --> 00:08:16,720
looking young

131
00:08:17,070 --> 00:08:17,900
isn't really surprising.

132
00:08:20,870 --> 00:08:21,310
Lord Geng,

133
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:23,270
the cause of death is unknown.

134
00:08:23,950 --> 00:08:25,270
I humbly request your permission

135
00:08:25,390 --> 00:08:25,830
for an autopsy.

136
00:08:26,690 --> 00:08:27,730
A body should not be casually examined.

137
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:29,920
We need the family's consent first.

138
00:08:30,830 --> 00:08:32,350
If the autopsy yielded no results,

139
00:08:32,559 --> 00:08:33,919
it would be difficult to explain to the family.

140
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:35,840
My lord,

141
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:38,030
I suspect this case

142
00:08:38,510 --> 00:08:39,150
is a poisoning.

143
00:08:41,650 --> 00:08:42,360
I've led a team to inspect

144
00:08:42,390 --> 00:08:43,240
the kitchen of Yanlai Restaurant.

145
00:08:43,630 --> 00:08:44,390
We found nothing unusual.

146
00:08:45,480 --> 00:08:46,550
Could it be that she

147
00:08:46,870 --> 00:08:47,850
died suddenly from an illness?

148
00:08:52,510 --> 00:08:53,000
Wen Jian,

149
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:55,120
what do you think?

150
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:56,440
My lord, I...

151
00:08:57,870 --> 00:08:58,720
I think I'd better

152
00:08:58,750 --> 00:08:59,540
not say anything.

153
00:09:00,510 --> 00:09:02,240
Feel free to express your opinions. Don't hesitate.

154
00:09:03,790 --> 00:09:04,150
My lord,

155
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:05,840
I believe

156
00:09:06,730 --> 00:09:07,810
this is the work of demons.

157
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:09,480
Whenever we encounter a difficult case,

158
00:09:09,510 --> 00:09:10,630
you always say it's the work of demons.

159
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:13,120
You said that female thief who slit throats last time

160
00:09:13,140 --> 00:09:14,150
was also a demon.

161
00:09:14,630 --> 00:09:15,090
But in the end?

162
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:17,330
In the end, I invited Xuanye to come out of seclusion

163
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:18,870
to eliminate that demon.

164
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:20,080
The lord is present here.

165
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:21,480
How dare you still spout such nonsense?

166
00:09:21,630 --> 00:09:23,360
It was the lord who said we should express our own views.

167
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:28,750
My lord,

168
00:09:29,010 --> 00:09:29,700
this corpse...

169
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:33,950
Next.

170
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:41,910
What's your name?

171
00:09:44,540 --> 00:09:45,450
Are you hungry?

172
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:46,670
I'll go buy you something to eat.

173
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:48,670
No need.

174
00:09:51,730 --> 00:09:52,330
It's my fault.

175
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:53,830
I didn't choose a good place to eat.

176
00:09:54,100 --> 00:09:56,000
Next time, I'll invite you to have dinner at my place

177
00:09:56,030 --> 00:09:56,910
as compensation.

178
00:09:58,270 --> 00:09:59,360
We're neighbors.

179
00:09:59,390 --> 00:10:00,390
We live very close to each other.

180
00:10:00,670 --> 00:10:01,910
You'll be there just by stepping out the door.

181
00:10:02,390 --> 00:10:03,410
My cooking skills are quite good.

182
00:10:06,030 --> 00:10:07,000
You really like cooking?

183
00:10:07,750 --> 00:10:08,570
I'm just cooking

184
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:10,000
for my savior.

185
00:10:14,480 --> 00:10:15,330
Last time I saw you

186
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:16,270
in Nanyang,

187
00:10:16,670 --> 00:10:17,750
you weren't like this at all.

188
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:19,120
Of course.

189
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:20,760
At that time,

190
00:10:20,790 --> 00:10:22,390
you were willing to help voluntarily.

191
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:24,120
Now that you're unwilling,

192
00:10:24,450 --> 00:10:25,640
my attitude naturally needs to have

193
00:10:25,670 --> 00:10:26,870
a slight change.

194
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:34,550
Next.

195
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:45,910
What's your name?

196
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:46,720
Chief Constable Wen.

197
00:10:46,740 --> 00:10:47,600
Are you finished?

198
00:10:47,670 --> 00:10:48,150
Not yet.

199
00:10:48,170 --> 00:10:49,550
I still need to go to Ganshan Clinic again.

200
00:10:50,080 --> 00:10:50,550
Hey, Xuanye.

201
00:10:52,550 --> 00:10:53,000
Xuanye?

202
00:10:53,480 --> 00:10:55,030
You... Why are you here?

203
00:10:57,150 --> 00:10:58,630
I went out for dinner last night

204
00:10:58,840 --> 00:10:59,510
and had bad luck,

205
00:10:59,530 --> 00:11:00,150
so...

206
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:03,240
You were also at Yanlai Restaurant last night?

207
00:11:04,080 --> 00:11:04,600
Yes.

208
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:05,790
That's perfect.

209
00:11:05,870 --> 00:11:06,480
I'm investigating

210
00:11:06,510 --> 00:11:07,240
the case at Yanlai Restaurant.

211
00:11:07,500 --> 00:11:08,200
Quick, follow me.

212
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:08,750
Let's meet with the lord.

213
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:13,750
Well...

214
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:16,910
She's with me.

215
00:11:18,550 --> 00:11:19,000
Alright then.

216
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:20,630
Let's go together.

217
00:11:33,930 --> 00:11:34,720
I've brought him here.

218
00:11:34,750 --> 00:11:35,320
Where are you going?

219
00:11:36,510 --> 00:11:37,120
Relying on him?

220
00:11:38,690 --> 00:11:39,410
I'd rather hope

221
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:40,200
the murderer would turn himself in.

222
00:11:42,720 --> 00:11:43,870
I don't have time for your nonsense.

223
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:48,440
Don't mind him.

224
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:56,320
The prefectural governor is inside.

225
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:57,550
Do you still want to go in?

226
00:12:00,150 --> 00:12:01,440
Then I'll wait for you outside.

227
00:12:15,190 --> 00:12:15,870
Wen Jian.

228
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:16,960
Tell Physician Jiu

229
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:18,120
about everything.

230
00:12:18,790 --> 00:12:19,440
Yes, my lord.

231
00:12:21,510 --> 00:12:22,000
This deceased person

232
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:23,870
was a dancer from Yunmen Dance Troupe.

233
00:12:24,200 --> 00:12:25,910
A few days ago, she suddenly became young again.

234
00:12:27,630 --> 00:12:28,320
This big box

235
00:12:28,390 --> 00:12:29,440
should be placed in the evidence room.

236
00:12:31,600 --> 00:12:32,440
I heard that

237
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:33,200
Physician Jiu from Ganshan Clinic has arrived.

238
00:12:33,750 --> 00:12:34,480
What's he here for?

239
00:12:36,030 --> 00:12:36,630
I don't know.

240
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:39,750
Be careful.

241
00:12:39,870 --> 00:12:40,750
The box is broken.

242
00:12:43,030 --> 00:12:43,960
Do you need help?

243
00:12:45,030 --> 00:12:45,600
Thank you.

244
00:12:47,800 --> 00:12:49,200
This case is really bizarre.

245
00:12:49,550 --> 00:12:51,600
I heard that the deceased actually transformed after death.

246
00:12:52,550 --> 00:12:53,240
What did she turn into?

247
00:12:53,750 --> 00:12:54,750
When she was brought back,

248
00:12:54,750 --> 00:12:55,670
she was still a young beauty.

249
00:12:56,080 --> 00:12:56,790
After a while,

250
00:12:56,870 --> 00:12:58,720
she turned into a mummified old woman.

251
00:12:58,840 --> 00:12:59,630
Seriously?

252
00:13:00,680 --> 00:13:01,760
See for yourself in a moment

253
00:13:01,790 --> 00:13:02,510
and you'll know.

254
00:13:12,990 --> 00:13:13,510
Thanks.

255
00:13:20,230 --> 00:13:21,390
That's pretty much how it happened.

256
00:13:23,240 --> 00:13:24,630
This case is indeed bizarre,

257
00:13:25,480 --> 00:13:26,840
but we can't be certain yet

258
00:13:26,860 --> 00:13:27,740
that it's the work of a demon.

259
00:13:29,910 --> 00:13:30,320
My lord,

260
00:13:30,960 --> 00:13:32,480
I need to go to the deceased's residence

261
00:13:32,670 --> 00:13:33,240
to investigate further.

262
00:13:34,910 --> 00:13:35,750
After the incident,

263
00:13:35,840 --> 00:13:36,510
I've already sent people

264
00:13:36,550 --> 00:13:37,960
to seal off the entire dance hall.

265
00:13:40,600 --> 00:13:42,080
You accompany Physician Jiu for another visit.

266
00:13:42,360 --> 00:13:43,150
Examine carefully.

267
00:13:43,850 --> 00:13:46,040
Even if it's truly the work of a demon,

268
00:13:46,410 --> 00:13:47,250
don't spread the word.

269
00:13:48,240 --> 00:13:48,670
Yes.

270
00:13:48,980 --> 00:13:49,650
Thank you, my lord.

271
00:13:55,630 --> 00:13:56,150
What are you looking for?

272
00:13:57,750 --> 00:13:58,200
Nothing.

273
00:13:58,630 --> 00:13:59,000
Let's go.

274
00:14:09,750 --> 00:14:10,960
Excuse me, officer.

275
00:14:11,960 --> 00:14:12,440
What is it?

276
00:14:12,630 --> 00:14:14,480
Can I take another look at that dressing mirror

277
00:14:14,500 --> 00:14:15,790
I picked up earlier?

278
00:14:18,080 --> 00:14:18,630
Why?

279
00:14:21,080 --> 00:14:22,870
Because I think it looks nice.

280
00:14:24,790 --> 00:14:25,240
Miss,

281
00:14:25,860 --> 00:14:27,580
these are all pieces of evidence.

282
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:30,120
Unauthorized personnel are not allowed to examine them.

283
00:14:31,320 --> 00:14:32,480
You'd better go home quickly.

284
00:14:56,840 --> 00:14:57,630
Officer,

285
00:14:58,320 --> 00:14:59,290
how's it going inside?

286
00:14:59,320 --> 00:15:00,690
When will Physician Jiu come out?

287
00:15:00,720 --> 00:15:01,200
Physician Jiu

288
00:15:01,390 --> 00:15:01,960
left a long time ago.

289
00:15:02,790 --> 00:15:03,560
Where did he go?

290
00:15:03,790 --> 00:15:04,790
Chief Constable Wen took him away.

291
00:15:04,920 --> 00:15:05,450
They were in a hurry.

292
00:15:05,480 --> 00:15:06,320
I think they went to investigate the case.

293
00:15:08,870 --> 00:15:09,480
Thank you.

294
00:15:13,480 --> 00:15:14,500
I can't explain it clearly anyway.

295
00:15:14,630 --> 00:15:15,670
Let's go in and take a look first.

296
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:18,520
It's here.

297
00:15:21,750 --> 00:15:22,240
Chief Constable Wen.

298
00:15:22,450 --> 00:15:24,260
This is the deceased Tian Rui's room.

299
00:15:51,240 --> 00:15:52,840
How long had it been since she last returned here?

300
00:15:54,090 --> 00:15:54,670
What's wrong?

301
00:15:56,100 --> 00:15:57,360
The tea strainer has grown small bugs.

302
00:15:57,960 --> 00:15:58,570
It seems she hadn't

303
00:15:58,600 --> 00:15:59,870
been back to clean for a long time.

304
00:16:02,240 --> 00:16:03,270
Their troupe leader said

305
00:16:03,270 --> 00:16:04,960
ever since Tian Rui had regained her youth,

306
00:16:04,960 --> 00:16:06,200
she had been pursued

307
00:16:06,220 --> 00:16:06,980
by the rich young men in the city.

308
00:16:07,630 --> 00:16:09,000
She sang and danced tirelessly day and night,

309
00:16:09,360 --> 00:16:10,200
and barely returned here.

310
00:16:18,030 --> 00:16:19,270
W-What is this?

311
00:16:20,720 --> 00:16:21,480
It's pear skin.

312
00:16:21,880 --> 00:16:22,360
Pear skin?

313
00:16:23,550 --> 00:16:24,590
Have you heard

314
00:16:24,730 --> 00:16:26,390
about the legend of the jade pear?

315
00:16:29,840 --> 00:16:31,320
It's said that if one sits alone

316
00:16:31,670 --> 00:16:33,390
in a closed room at midnight,

317
00:16:33,960 --> 00:16:34,910
face a mirror,

318
00:16:35,320 --> 00:16:36,120
light two candles,

319
00:16:36,600 --> 00:16:37,510
and peel a pear

320
00:16:37,790 --> 00:16:39,670
while reciting the jade pear nursery rhyme,

321
00:16:39,870 --> 00:16:40,790
then if the pear skin

322
00:16:41,030 --> 00:16:42,120
remains intact after reciting,

323
00:16:42,440 --> 00:16:43,550
one can summon

324
00:16:43,570 --> 00:16:44,480
the pear-delivering demon.

325
00:16:54,240 --> 00:16:56,320
This jade pear is also called the rejuvenating pear.

326
00:16:57,080 --> 00:16:57,990
Once consumed,

327
00:16:58,210 --> 00:16:59,440
it can restore youth overnight.

328
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:01,910
Restore youth overnight?

329
00:17:02,550 --> 00:17:03,150
That does match up.

330
00:17:03,960 --> 00:17:05,380
Tian Rui had always been passionate about

331
00:17:05,400 --> 00:17:06,550
methods for maintaining health and beauty,

332
00:17:06,880 --> 00:17:08,000
but they'd never been very effective.

333
00:17:09,030 --> 00:17:10,400
You think she ate the jade pear?

334
00:17:12,589 --> 00:17:13,160
Perhaps.

335
00:17:15,599 --> 00:17:16,550
Where is her body?

336
00:17:17,480 --> 00:17:18,240
Still at the government office.

337
00:17:18,640 --> 00:17:20,130
Youhuang knows the lord is looking for you to solve the case.

338
00:17:20,160 --> 00:17:21,589
He absolutely refuses to give me the key to the mortuary.

339
00:17:21,750 --> 00:17:22,680
I'll go see the lord again tomorrow morning.

340
00:17:23,510 --> 00:17:24,109
We can't wait.

341
00:17:24,990 --> 00:17:25,800
Tell Chi Xue to go.

342
00:17:41,750 --> 00:17:43,400
This mirror has a time limit.

343
00:17:44,500 --> 00:17:46,000
If I don't go now, it'll be too late.

344
00:17:56,750 --> 00:17:58,440
But if I tell him directly,

345
00:17:58,440 --> 00:17:59,790
he might not believe me.

346
00:18:02,310 --> 00:18:03,310
Never mind all that.

347
00:18:05,830 --> 00:18:06,590
Friend, I'm leaving.

348
00:18:07,550 --> 00:18:08,480
Let's get a drink another day.

349
00:19:10,590 --> 00:19:11,590
They're asleep?

350
00:19:49,830 --> 00:19:50,880
Are you following me?

351
00:20:11,590 --> 00:20:12,160
I see.

352
00:20:13,310 --> 00:20:14,790
She must have taken an immortality elixir.

353
00:20:16,960 --> 00:20:17,350
Yes.

354
00:20:17,830 --> 00:20:18,310
Chief,

355
00:20:18,510 --> 00:20:19,200
you guessed right.

356
00:20:20,150 --> 00:20:20,750
Um,

357
00:20:21,310 --> 00:20:22,510
can I go home now?

358
00:20:22,690 --> 00:20:23,380
Wait a moment.

359
00:20:24,400 --> 00:20:25,480
According to this book,

360
00:20:26,510 --> 00:20:27,560
in ancient times, there was someone called

361
00:20:27,590 --> 00:20:28,440
Chi Songzi

362
00:20:29,160 --> 00:20:29,790
who consumed a type of

363
00:20:29,810 --> 00:20:31,690
immortality elixir called Ice Jade Powder.

364
00:20:32,310 --> 00:20:33,750
From then on, he became immortal.

365
00:20:34,000 --> 00:20:35,070
He could even control the wind and rain.

366
00:20:38,790 --> 00:20:39,880
There was also someone named Peng Zu

367
00:20:40,030 --> 00:20:41,000
who took an immortality elixir

368
00:20:41,720 --> 00:20:42,880
and lived for over 800 years.

369
00:20:45,070 --> 00:20:46,480
In more recent times,

370
00:20:47,240 --> 00:20:48,280
there was a Taoist priest in Hongzhou

371
00:20:48,310 --> 00:20:49,350
with the surname Hu

372
00:20:49,720 --> 00:20:51,960
who claimed to have taken an immortality pill

373
00:20:52,240 --> 00:20:53,550
and lived for over 400 years.

374
00:20:54,060 --> 00:20:55,300
It's said he's still alive today.

375
00:20:56,740 --> 00:20:57,850
However, the old man

376
00:20:57,880 --> 00:20:59,070
likes to travel all over the world,

377
00:20:59,480 --> 00:21:01,000
making it difficult for ordinary people to find him.

378
00:21:02,510 --> 00:21:02,960
Chief,

379
00:21:03,750 --> 00:21:04,310
that's it?

380
00:21:04,920 --> 00:21:05,480
You believe this?

381
00:21:05,680 --> 00:21:06,910
Of course I don't believe it.

382
00:21:07,750 --> 00:21:09,030
If such a miraculous medicine really existed,

383
00:21:09,790 --> 00:21:11,400
how could there still be dynastic changes

384
00:21:11,590 --> 00:21:12,920
and transfers of power?

385
00:21:15,160 --> 00:21:15,720
I don't believe it,

386
00:21:16,160 --> 00:21:17,400
but that doesn't mean others don't.

387
00:21:17,960 --> 00:21:18,750
This book mentions

388
00:21:19,640 --> 00:21:20,920
that some people, in pursuit of immortality,

389
00:21:21,150 --> 00:21:22,090
become obsessed with elixirs

390
00:21:22,430 --> 00:21:24,690
and ultimately die from poisoning

391
00:21:25,110 --> 00:21:25,930
while bleeding profusely.

392
00:21:30,110 --> 00:21:31,440
Tian Rui's corpse

393
00:21:31,840 --> 00:21:32,940
aged instantly,

394
00:21:33,310 --> 00:21:34,160
which is indeed strange.

395
00:21:36,960 --> 00:21:38,590
I know that nowadays there are some alchemists

396
00:21:39,030 --> 00:21:40,180
who do possess certain skills.

397
00:21:40,500 --> 00:21:41,480
They can't produce

398
00:21:41,510 --> 00:21:42,880
immortality elixirs,

399
00:21:43,410 --> 00:21:44,040
but they can concoct

400
00:21:44,070 --> 00:21:45,480
temporarily effective poison pills.

401
00:21:46,720 --> 00:21:47,650
Perhaps Tian Rui

402
00:21:48,440 --> 00:21:50,030
bought one of their pills.

403
00:21:55,110 --> 00:21:55,960
Grab your things

404
00:21:56,560 --> 00:21:57,310
and come with me.

405
00:21:58,160 --> 00:21:58,680
Where are we going?

406
00:22:01,240 --> 00:22:01,960
To the mortuary

407
00:22:02,720 --> 00:22:03,350
for an autopsy.

408
00:22:17,810 --> 00:22:18,570
Xuanye!

409
00:22:23,230 --> 00:22:23,800
Hurry up.

410
00:22:28,140 --> 00:22:29,320
Doing this so late

411
00:22:29,490 --> 00:22:30,380
is such a sin.

412
00:22:38,750 --> 00:22:39,440
Well done.

413
00:22:41,920 --> 00:22:42,560
Did you encounter

414
00:22:42,590 --> 00:22:43,440
any trouble on the way?

415
00:22:44,790 --> 00:22:45,590
No trouble,

416
00:22:46,400 --> 00:22:47,240
but there was a surprise.

417
00:22:48,200 --> 00:22:48,920
What surprise?

418
00:22:49,480 --> 00:22:50,720
I met Manniang's sister-in-law.

419
00:22:54,830 --> 00:22:55,790
You met Banxia?

420
00:22:56,000 --> 00:22:56,400
Yes.

421
00:22:57,350 --> 00:22:58,310
How did you run into her?

422
00:22:58,910 --> 00:22:59,430
I don't know.

423
00:23:01,240 --> 00:23:01,960
What was she doing?

424
00:23:02,350 --> 00:23:02,880
Following me.

425
00:23:04,240 --> 00:23:05,170
Why would she follow you?

426
00:23:05,830 --> 00:23:06,400
To play with me.

427
00:23:07,830 --> 00:23:08,750
Play with you?

428
00:23:12,640 --> 00:23:13,400
What did you do?

429
00:23:13,790 --> 00:23:14,550
I played with her too.

430
00:23:15,720 --> 00:23:17,160
She followed me, trying to scare me,

431
00:23:17,550 --> 00:23:18,880
so I left her in the mortuary.

432
00:23:18,940 --> 00:23:19,690
I scared her back.

433
00:23:32,480 --> 00:23:32,960
Yan Li.

434
00:23:33,400 --> 00:23:34,030
Yan Li.

435
00:23:34,400 --> 00:23:35,350
Why did you fall asleep?

436
00:23:46,440 --> 00:23:47,000
Chief.

437
00:23:48,160 --> 00:23:48,880
If you want to sleep,

438
00:23:49,700 --> 00:23:50,980
do it at home after resigning.

439
00:23:51,590 --> 00:23:52,020
I wouldn't dare.

440
00:23:52,070 --> 00:23:52,500
I wouldn't dare.

441
00:23:53,510 --> 00:23:54,680
Next time I catch you...

442
00:23:54,970 --> 00:23:55,940
Chief, there won't be a next time.

443
00:23:56,070 --> 00:23:56,920
There won't be a next time, Chief Constable.

444
00:23:57,680 --> 00:23:58,550
I'm going to work now.

445
00:24:01,270 --> 00:24:01,720
Wait a moment.

446
00:24:04,110 --> 00:24:05,480
You're on duty at the mortuary today, right?

447
00:24:05,680 --> 00:24:06,240
Yes, Chief Constable.

448
00:24:06,920 --> 00:24:07,640
Open the door for me.

449
00:24:08,090 --> 00:24:08,650
Remember this.

450
00:24:09,430 --> 00:24:10,480
Before we come out,

451
00:24:10,750 --> 00:24:11,540
you stay here and guard.

452
00:24:11,720 --> 00:24:12,000
Yes.

453
00:24:12,110 --> 00:24:13,000
Don't let anyone in.

454
00:24:13,090 --> 00:24:13,640
Yes, Chief Constable.

455
00:24:19,350 --> 00:24:19,880
She followed me.

456
00:24:19,900 --> 00:24:20,580
She was trying to scare me,

457
00:24:21,160 --> 00:24:22,400
so I left her in the mortuary.

458
00:24:22,500 --> 00:24:23,260
I scared her back.

459
00:24:28,400 --> 00:24:28,750
Chief.

460
00:24:29,310 --> 00:24:30,340
If the lord asks tomorrow...

461
00:25:02,030 --> 00:25:02,680
Constable Li,

462
00:25:04,030 --> 00:25:05,510
have you ever seen in all these years

463
00:25:06,190 --> 00:25:07,620
a poison that can age someone overnight?

464
00:25:09,030 --> 00:25:09,480
No.

465
00:25:13,030 --> 00:25:14,510
If no poison is found in the stomach,

466
00:25:15,400 --> 00:25:16,240
what should we do?

467
00:25:18,110 --> 00:25:19,720
It could have been injected externally.

468
00:25:20,370 --> 00:25:22,080
Skin, blood, and hair

469
00:25:22,110 --> 00:25:22,640
all can be tested.

470
00:25:23,790 --> 00:25:24,480
However,

471
00:25:25,240 --> 00:25:26,440
she's been dead for a day.

472
00:25:26,720 --> 00:25:27,350
It might be difficult.

473
00:25:31,160 --> 00:25:32,200
Let's extract the stomach first.

474
00:26:39,000 --> 00:26:39,550
Who's there?

475
00:26:52,000 --> 00:26:52,540
Let's go back.

476
00:26:53,080 --> 00:26:53,580
Alright.

477
00:26:59,170 --> 00:26:59,720
Chief!

478
00:27:01,110 --> 00:27:01,830
The body is missing.

479
00:27:18,550 --> 00:27:19,110
Find it!

480
00:27:29,200 --> 00:27:29,790
It's alright now.

481
00:27:51,240 --> 00:27:52,400
Come, put this on.

482
00:28:02,880 --> 00:28:04,240
What were you doing at the government office?

483
00:28:07,440 --> 00:28:08,720
This case is extremely tricky.

484
00:28:09,000 --> 00:28:10,430
The culprit is likely to kill again.

485
00:28:10,720 --> 00:28:11,790
I must investigate first.

486
00:28:12,790 --> 00:28:13,590
As your father's matter,

487
00:28:13,830 --> 00:28:14,870
I've kept it in mind.

488
00:28:22,720 --> 00:28:23,110
We're here.

489
00:28:24,590 --> 00:28:25,350
Where are you going?

490
00:28:35,240 --> 00:28:36,070
About tonight,

491
00:28:36,790 --> 00:28:37,550
I'm sorry.

492
00:29:10,210 --> 00:29:10,790
Xuanye,

493
00:29:10,940 --> 00:29:11,730
do you want some radish?

494
00:29:19,960 --> 00:29:20,830
Rest up.

495
00:29:46,240 --> 00:29:47,000
Xuanye!

496
00:29:48,550 --> 00:29:49,550
Jiu Xuanye!

497
00:29:50,680 --> 00:29:51,720
Jiu Xuanye!

498
00:29:52,590 --> 00:29:53,550
Jiu Xuanye!

499
00:29:56,070 --> 00:29:56,750
Xuanye!

500
00:29:58,750 --> 00:29:59,440
Xuanye!

501
00:30:00,790 --> 00:30:01,720
Jiu Xuanye!

502
00:30:02,550 --> 00:30:04,080
I know you can hear me.

503
00:30:04,110 --> 00:30:05,240
I have something to tell you.

504
00:30:07,790 --> 00:30:08,680
Jiu Xuanye!

505
00:30:13,640 --> 00:30:14,240
Xuanye!

506
00:30:15,510 --> 00:30:16,480
Jiu Xuanye!

507
00:30:18,310 --> 00:30:19,080
Jiu Xuanye!

508
00:30:19,110 --> 00:30:19,920
Stop yelling.

509
00:30:34,440 --> 00:30:35,280
Why are you here?

510
00:30:36,030 --> 00:30:37,200
Didn't you call for me?

511
00:30:39,480 --> 00:30:40,790
I didn't call you to come over.

512
00:30:42,920 --> 00:30:43,510
Besides,

513
00:30:43,510 --> 00:30:45,030
couldn't you have given me a heads up before coming?

514
00:30:49,480 --> 00:30:50,630
What did you want to see me about?

515
00:30:57,590 --> 00:30:58,550
If you don't say it, I'm leaving.

516
00:31:01,780 --> 00:31:02,410
Wait.

517
00:31:16,500 --> 00:31:16,930
Yes,

518
00:31:18,600 --> 00:31:19,400
I'm not as capable as you.

519
00:31:20,880 --> 00:31:22,480
But compared to ordinary people,

520
00:31:23,170 --> 00:31:23,800
I should be considered as

521
00:31:23,830 --> 00:31:24,960
quite knowledgeable, right?

522
00:31:25,640 --> 00:31:27,460
Over the years, I've seen flying fish,

523
00:31:27,650 --> 00:31:28,830
talking spiders,

524
00:31:28,850 --> 00:31:29,850
children with tails,

525
00:31:30,030 --> 00:31:31,160
and butterflies that can pass through walls.

526
00:31:32,070 --> 00:31:33,480
Aren't they all strange

527
00:31:33,480 --> 00:31:34,240
and unique?

528
00:31:37,200 --> 00:31:38,110
I just want to ask you.

529
00:31:39,240 --> 00:31:40,470
Are mirrors that don't reflect people

530
00:31:40,490 --> 00:31:41,700
also very common?

531
00:31:44,280 --> 00:31:46,040
There was one at the fire scene in Nanyang City,

532
00:31:46,310 --> 00:31:47,640
one in my father's room,

533
00:31:48,110 --> 00:31:49,510
and also on at the restaurant in Guangping City.

534
00:31:49,880 --> 00:31:50,760
Why is it that whenever it appears,

535
00:31:50,790 --> 00:31:51,880
there's a murder?

536
00:31:56,030 --> 00:31:56,590
I know.

537
00:31:58,590 --> 00:31:59,440
You don't believe me.

538
00:32:01,640 --> 00:32:03,510
You think I'm just missing my father

539
00:32:05,200 --> 00:32:06,160
and making a fuss.

540
00:32:09,400 --> 00:32:10,160
But now,

541
00:32:10,160 --> 00:32:11,400
the evidence is right here.

542
00:32:13,410 --> 00:32:14,060
If you don't believe me,

543
00:32:14,080 --> 00:32:15,450
you should at least believe the evidence, right?

544
00:32:19,640 --> 00:32:20,790
You went to the government office just now

545
00:32:21,350 --> 00:32:22,440
to get this?

546
00:32:26,720 --> 00:32:27,960
The workers said

547
00:32:29,400 --> 00:32:30,880
it belonged to the dancer from last night.

548
00:32:36,030 --> 00:32:37,160
I will follow this lead

549
00:32:37,160 --> 00:32:38,030
and continue investigating.

550
00:32:38,590 --> 00:32:40,110
As soon as I have any news about your father,

551
00:32:40,640 --> 00:32:41,960
I'll let you know immediately.

552
00:32:43,750 --> 00:32:44,250
Wait.

553
00:32:45,030 --> 00:32:45,590
That's it?

554
00:32:46,640 --> 00:32:47,680
What else do you want?

555
00:32:51,590 --> 00:32:52,320
I want to be involved in

556
00:32:52,350 --> 00:32:53,240
the Yanlai Restaurant case.

557
00:32:53,960 --> 00:32:55,160
I want to find the killer with you.

558
00:32:56,510 --> 00:32:57,980
This matter involves demons.

559
00:32:58,210 --> 00:32:59,040
The dangers involved

560
00:32:59,070 --> 00:33:00,030
are beyond your imagination.

561
00:33:01,110 --> 00:33:01,960
If we find

562
00:33:01,960 --> 00:33:03,310
the murderer who killed the dancer,

563
00:33:03,510 --> 00:33:04,960
we can locate my father's whereabouts.

564
00:33:07,240 --> 00:33:08,240
So even if what lies ahead

565
00:33:08,240 --> 00:33:09,480
is a den of monstrous beasts,

566
00:33:11,030 --> 00:33:12,440
I will still risk my life to venture forth.

567
00:33:28,200 --> 00:33:28,830
Do you like it?

568
00:33:30,750 --> 00:33:31,480
Didn't I just

569
00:33:31,480 --> 00:33:32,350
eat one recently?

570
00:33:32,660 --> 00:33:34,920
[Chi Wangchuan]

571
00:33:32,920 --> 00:33:35,110
It won't hurt to have another one.

572
00:33:36,400 --> 00:33:37,030
You said before

573
00:33:37,590 --> 00:33:38,400
that one jade pear

574
00:33:38,480 --> 00:33:39,790
can maintain one's beauty for a year.

575
00:33:40,270 --> 00:33:41,550
I just had one recently.

576
00:33:41,880 --> 00:33:43,440
Why did you murder for a pear again?

577
00:33:43,920 --> 00:33:44,640
Especially...

578
00:33:45,550 --> 00:33:46,960
Especially murdering Tian Rui.

579
00:33:47,240 --> 00:33:48,070
She was jealous of you.

580
00:33:48,480 --> 00:33:49,350
She talked behind your back.

581
00:33:49,960 --> 00:33:51,200
Shouldn't I have killed her?

582
00:33:51,790 --> 00:33:52,350
But you...

583
00:33:52,350 --> 00:33:53,240
But what?

584
00:33:53,880 --> 00:33:54,880
You didn't even like her.

585
00:34:00,590 --> 00:34:01,240
Alright.

