699
00:38:32,840 --> 00:38:34,010
The mother pear will absorb

700
00:38:34,040 --> 00:38:35,000
the vitality of the deceased.

701
00:38:35,480 --> 00:38:36,440
If taken at this moment,

702
00:38:36,880 --> 00:38:38,150
not only can it restore youth,

703
00:38:38,560 --> 00:38:39,040
but it also

704
00:38:39,070 --> 00:38:40,030
